            <TYPE_CONTRACT CTYPE="WORKS"/>
            <SHORT_DESCR>
               <P>LCC is undertaking a procurement exercise for the provision of a highway maintenance contract to replace the current Lincolnshire Highways Alliance which is due to reach full term on the 31.3.2020. The procurement includes 3 lots:</P>
               <P>Lot 1: Highway Works.</P>
               <P>Lot 2: Traffic Signals.</P>
               <P>Lot 3: Design Services.</P>
               <P>It is anticipated that the contract term for each Lot will be 6 years starting from the 1.4.2020 with the opportunity to extend the contract for an additional six years to a maximum term of 12 years.</P>
               <P>As part of the commissioning cycle LCC is keen to test the direction of travel with the market prior to commencing the formal procurement process. To do this we are proposing to hold a Meet the Buyer Day and would request that all interested parties register interest.</P>
               <P>Please see additional information for details of our “Meet the Buyer” event.</P>
            </SHORT_DESCR>
            <VAL_ESTIMATED_TOTAL CURRENCY="GBP">762000000</VAL_ESTIMATED_TOTAL>
