         <COMPLEMENTARY_INFO>
            <INFO_ADD>
               <P>LCC is keen to test the direction of travel with the market prior to commencing the formal procurement process. To do this LCC are proposing to hold a Meet the Buyer Day and would request that all interested parties register interest.</P>
               <P>The event will provide an opportunity for interested parties to find out more about the Highway Service, the procurement process and discuss the approach LCC is proposing.</P>
               <P>Date and venue information: 18.5.2018, 9:00 to 17:00.</P>
               <P>Location: Lincoln.</P>
               <P>Refreshments and Lunch will be provided.</P>
               <P>Parking is available on site.</P>
               <P>To book your place, please e-mail Highways2020@lincolnshire.gov.uk</P>
               <P>Due to availability, spaces are limited to 2 representatives per organisation on a first come, first served basis. In the event that it is oversubscribed, LCC may consider providing additional discussion slots at a later date if capacity allows. All material provided on the day will be made available to all prospective tenderers via ProContract.</P>
            </INFO_ADD>
